  "title": "WAITER / WAITRESS",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Welcoming and seating guests</li><li>Taking food and beverage orders from guests</li><li>Having knowledge of the general wine, beer, and alcoholic beverages the club serves</li><li>Able to give suggestions based on customers' preference</li><li>Always maintain a clean and tidy area</li><li>Handling multiple tables and tasks in an efficient manner.</li><li>Transport is provided</li><li>Assist in any ad-hoc tasks assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide excellent customer service in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Proactive, team player</li><li>Exceptional interpersonal & communication skills</li><li>Able to work nights, weekends and holidays</li><li>Approachable, with a professional appearance</li><li>Have an eye for detail and understanding guests' needs</li></ul>",
